item.title: COVID19 API
item.description: API for exploring covid-19 cases around the globe powered by FastAPI framework Link https://nat236919.github.io/covid19-api/ Introduction This API provides the information regarding ‘2019 Novel Coronavirus (covid-19)’. It contains a number of confirmed, death, and recovered cases based on the data provided by the Johns Hopkins University Center for Systems Science and Engineering (JHU CSSE) Features The current data (daily updated) Confirmed, Deaths, Recovered The affected countries Individual affected country Timeseries Examples: https://covid2019-api.
